{"id":"api/common/DecimalPipe","title":"DecimalPipe","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common/DecimalPipe\", \"name\": \"DecimalPipe\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L15-L146\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/15.0.1/packages/common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts#L15-L146\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"decimalpipe\">DecimalPipe<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe#decimalpipe\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label pipe\">pipe</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">根据数字选项和区域设置规则格式化值。区域设置确定组的大小和分隔符、小数点字符和其他特定于区域设置的配置。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Formats a value according to digit options and locale rules.\nLocale determines group sizing and separator,\ndecimal point character, and other locale-specific configurations.</p>\n\n\n  </section>\n\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"pipe-overview\">\n  <code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">{{ value_expression | <span class=\"kwd nocode\">number</span> [ : digitsInfo [ : locale ] ] }}</code-example>\n\n  \n<h2 id=\"导出自\">导出自<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe#导出自\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">CommonModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n  <h2 id=\"input-value\">输入值<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe#input-value\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table pipe-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>value</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string | number</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">要格式化的值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The value to be formatted.</p>\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h2 id=\"parameters\">参数<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe#parameters\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table pipe-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>digitsInfo</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">设置数字和十进制表示。<a href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe#digitsinfo\">查看更多</a>。</p><p translation-result=\"on\">可选值。默认值为 <code>undefined</code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Sets digit and decimal representation.\n<a href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe#digitsinfo\">See more</a>.</p>\n\n\n        \n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>locale</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p translation-result=\"on\">指定要使用的区域设置格式规则。<a href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe#locale\">查看更多</a>。</p><p translation-result=\"on\">可选值。默认值为 <code>undefined</code>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Specifies what locale format rules to use.\n<a href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe#locale\">See more</a>.</p>\n\n\n        \n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n</section>\n\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><p><code><a href=\"api/common/formatNumber\" class=\"code-anchor\">formatNumber</a>()</code></p></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <h3 id=\"digitsinfo\" translation-result=\"on\">数字信息<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe#digitsinfo\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3><h3 translation-origin=\"off\">digitsInfo<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe#digitsinfo\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">值的十进制表示由 <code>digitsInfo</code> 参数指定，用以下格式编写：<br></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The value's decimal representation is specified by the <code>digitsInfo</code>\nparameter, written in the following format:<br></p>\n\n<code-example>\n{minIntegerDigits}.{minFractionDigits}-{maxFractionDigits}\n</code-example>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><code>minIntegerDigits</code> ：小数点前的最小整数位数。默认值为 1。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>minIntegerDigits</code>:\nThe minimum number of integer digits before the decimal point.\nDefault is 1.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><code>minFractionDigits</code> ：小数点后的最小位数。默认值为 0。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>minFractionDigits</code>:\nThe minimum number of digits after the decimal point.\nDefault is 0.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><code>maxFractionDigits</code> ：小数点后的最大位数。默认值为 3。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>maxFractionDigits</code>:\nThe maximum number of digits after the decimal point.\nDefault is 3.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">如果格式化的值被截断，将使用“to-nearest”方法将其四舍五入：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">If the formatted value is truncated it will be rounded using the \"to-nearest\" method:</p>\n\n<code-example>\n{{3.6 | number: '1.0-0'}}\n&lt;!--will output '4'--&gt;\n\n{{-3.6 | number:'1.0-0'}}\n&lt;!--will output '-4'--&gt;\n</code-example>\n<h3 id=\"locale\" translation-result=\"on\">语言环境<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe#locale\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3><h3 translation-origin=\"off\">locale<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe#locale\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><code>locale</code>\n将根据区域设置规则格式化值。区域设置确定组的大小和分隔符、小数点字符和其他特定于区域设置的配置。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>locale</code> will format a value according to locale rules.\nLocale determines group sizing and separator,\ndecimal point character, and other locale-specific configurations.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">未提供时，使用 <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> 的值，默认为 <code>en-US</code> 。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">When not supplied, uses the value of <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code>, which is <code>en-US</code> by default.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">请参阅<a href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id\">设置你的应用程序区域设置</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">See <a href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id\">Setting your app locale</a>.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"example\" translation-result=\"on\">例子<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3><h3 translation-origin=\"off\">Example<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">以下代码显示了管道如何根据各种格式规范转换值，其中调用者的默认区域设置是 <code>en-US</code> 。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The following code shows how the pipe transforms values\naccording to various format specifications,\nwhere the caller's default locale is <code>en-US</code>.</p>\n\n<code-example path=\"common/pipes/ts/number_pipe.ts\" region=\"NumberPipe\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'number-pipe',\n  template: `&lt;div&gt;\n\n    &lt;p&gt;\n      No specified formatting:\n      {{pi | number}}\n      &lt;!--output: '3.142'--&gt;\n    &lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;p&gt;\n      With digitsInfo parameter specified:\n      {{pi | number:'4.1-5'}}\n      &lt;!--output: '0,003.14159'--&gt;\n    &lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;p&gt;\n      With digitsInfo and\n      locale parameters specified:\n      {{pi | number:'4.1-5':'fr'}}\n      &lt;!--output: '0 003,14159'--&gt;\n    &lt;/p&gt;\n\n  &lt;/div&gt;`\n})\nexport class NumberPipeComponent {\n  pi: number = 3.14159265359;\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/common/formatCurrency\n - api/common/formatNumber\n - api/common/formatPercent\n - api/core/PipeTransform\n - guide/ajs-quick-reference\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\n - guide/pipes\n - guide/pipes-overview\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/common/DecimalPipe#decimalpipe\n - api/common/DecimalPipe#digitsinfo\n - api/common/DecimalPipe#example\n - api/common/DecimalPipe#input-value\n - api/common/DecimalPipe#locale\n - api/common/DecimalPipe#parameters\n - api/common/DecimalPipe#see-also\n - api/common/DecimalPipe#usage-notes\n - api/common/DecimalPipe#例子\n - api/common/DecimalPipe#导出自\n - api/common/DecimalPipe#数字信息\n - api/common/DecimalPipe#语言环境\n - api/common/formatNumber\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/LOCALE_ID\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L15-L146\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/15.0.1/packages/common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts#L15-L146\n-->"}